  "instructions": [
    "Soak the red kidney beans overnight and pressure cook them until tender.",
    "In a pan, heat ghee and saut\u00142; the breadcrumbs until lightly toasted.",
    "Add ferment jang and cook for another minute.",
    "Add smoked paprika, ground cumin, turmeric powder, red chili powder, and salt. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cooked beans, water, roasted cumin seeds, and lemon juice. Mix well.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a robata grill and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Serve hot garnished with chopped cilantro (if using)."
